import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    sns.set_style("darkgrid")
    ax = sns.lineplot(x="date", y="wounds", data=data, color='blue')
    ax.set(xlabel='Date', ylabel='Wounds')
    ax.axhline(y=data['wounds'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Mean')
    plt.title('What is the trend of wounds over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.dropna()
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='disease', color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['disease'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.xlabel('Disease Cases')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of disease cases?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['wounds', 'other']]
    data = data.sum()
    plt.bar(data.index, data.values)
    plt.title('What is the proportion of wounds to other injuries?', wrap=True)
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.xlabel('Injury Type')
    plt.legend(['Wounds', 'Other'])
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    data['year'] = data['date'].dt.year
    data['month'] = data['date'].dt.month
    data['total_injuries'] = data['wounds'] + data['other'] + data['disease']
    data = data.groupby(['year', 'month'])['total_injuries'].sum().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='month', y='total_injuries', hue='year', data=data, ax=ax, palette='Set2')
    ax.set_xlabel('Month')
    ax.set_ylabel('Total Injuries')
    ax.set_title('What is the total number of injuries over time?')
    ax.legend(title='Year', loc='upper left')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
